WEBVTT

00:00:01.166 --> 00:00:03.439
Dok mi je mama objašnjavala nešto

00:00:03.463 --> 00:00:05.254
o baki i odrastanju,

00:00:05.278 --> 00:00:06.985
ali nisam se
mogao usredotočiti na nju

00:00:07.009 --> 00:00:09.941
jer sam imao pet godina
i bio sam prestravljen.

00:00:09.965 --> 00:00:12.950
Bio sam upravo vidio Zelenu damu.

00:00:12.974 --> 00:00:15.973
Tjedan prije toga,
gledao sam film "Godzillu",

00:00:15.997 --> 00:00:19.144
onaj gdje ogromna zvijer
u obliku guštera razara veliki grad

00:00:19.168 --> 00:00:23.485
i pomisao da me napada zeleno
čudovište, urezala mi se u pamćenje.

00:00:23.850 --> 00:00:27.139
Bio sam tamo, na vrhu
Donjeg Manhattana s mamom,

00:00:27.163 --> 00:00:28.944
piljeći u nju:

00:00:28.968 --> 00:00:30.127
u njezine rogove,